reviewText: This is one of my wife's favorite movies. And I like it every time I watch it. There's a certain charm to Hailey Mills movies that makes me want to watch them over and over.  That's why I like her version of "The Parent Trap" better than the reremake with Lindsey Lohan. Hard as Disney may have tried to surpass their original classic, they just couldn't.
I bought these as a gift for someone who loves to remember our childhood sitting in front of the black and white Zeineth with the whole family on a Sunday afternoon. AWESOME!
I love that I can see these again.

From the first time I saw these  two movies, I always wanted to purchase them. Now even after all these years they are still
as fresh as the first time i saw them, they are great for the whole family, good wholesome fun for everyone.
I recommend the two movies to everyone.
I watched the movie for the first time when I was about 15 years old. I really enjoyed the comedy of the movie. It's just a great movie for any girl at heart.
I remember seeing these movies as a young girl and still enjoy them.  Was pleased to see I could purchase both of these movies for a low price.
Two of my favorite movies from my youth.
